DESIGNATE
  Change what a sector produces by reassigning its type.

SYNTAX
  designate <sects> <type-letter>
  desi      <sects> <type-letter>
  des       <sects> <type-letter>

DESCRIPTION
  Sets the designation of one or more sectors.  After redesignation
  the sector starts building toward 100% efficiency; productivity
  requires >=60% efficiency, which takes several update cycles.

  You can only designate sectors you own.  Designating a sector does
  not affect its population or stockpiles.

  Common designations:
    c  capital           a  agribusiness (food)
    g  gold mine         m  iron mine
    o  oil field         j  light manufacturing (LCM)
    k  heavy manuf (HCM) h  harbor (ships)
    *  airfield          e  enlistment center
    t  tech center       r  research lab
    l  library (edu)     +  highway
    -  wasteland

  See 'info sector-types' for the full list.

EXAMPLE
  des 4,-2 a                grow food at 4,-2
  des -4,2 m                mine iron at -4,2
  des 6,0 h                 build a harbor at 6,0
  des 1,-3 e                enlistment center for military

SEE ALSO
  sector-types  resource  census  show  build
